.SH "SYNOPSIS"
Here you will find a list of all the available topics for help related to \fBDalma\fR and how to call for help
.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Users can request help on any specific topic using the following command:
.
.P
\fBman dalma\-<topic>\fR
.
.SS "where \'topic\' can be one of:"
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
storage \fI\.\./html/dalma\-storage\.html\fR : Display information about the different filesystems and how to use them
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fIqueues\fR \fI\.\./html/dalma\-queues\.html\fR : Display the different queues information and when to use them
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fImodules\fR : NYUME modules description\. How to access to the available software in the system
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fIvisualisation\fR : Do you have any visualisation needs ?
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fIsoftware\fR : List of the available software
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fIhardware\fR : Hardware description
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fIlogin\fR : How to log into the system, from inside and outside NYUAD
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fIcompiling\fR : Compilation best practices and guidelines
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fIpolicies\fR : Want to know the limits that affect you according to NYU policies ?
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fIdebugging\fR : How to debug your code
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fIget_account\fR : Requesting/renewing an account in Dalma
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fIdata_movement\fR : How to move data efficiently in/out Dalma
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fIjob_monitoring\fR : How to monitor your job
.
.IP "" 0
.
